About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. ‚ÄúAlpha‚Äù, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

Welcome to our Tamil Devotional Channel, your ultimate destination for soulful and uplifting Tamil devotional songs. Dive into the divine with our carefully curated collections designed to inspire and bring peace to your soul every day of the week.

Daily Devotional Songs:
* Monday Tamil Devotional Songs
* Tuesday Tamil Devotional Songs
* Wednesday Tamil Devotional Songs
* Thursday Tamil Devotional Songs
* Friday Tamil Devotional Songs

* Sunday Tamil Devotional Songs

Special Devotional Collections:
* Shiva Tamil Devotional Songs: Celebrate the power and grace of Lord Shiva.
* Vishnu Tamil Devotional Songs: Immerse in the blessings of Lord Vishnu.
* Muruga Tamil Devotional Songs: Invoke the valor and blessings of Lord Muruga.
* Hanuman Tamil Devotional Songs: Feel the strength and devotion of Lord Hanuman.
* Amman Tamil Devotional Songs: Honor the divine mother in her various forms.
* Saibaba Tamil Devotional Songs: Seek the blessings of Shirdi Sai Baba.
* Balaji Tamil Devotional Songs: Worship Lord Venkateswara with these soulful songs.
* Lakshmi Tamil Devotional Songs: Attract prosperity with hymns for Goddess Lakshmi.
* Devi Tamil Devotional Songs: Praise the supreme goddess Devi in her many avatars.
* Ganesh Tamil Devotional Songs: Start your day with prayers to Lord Ganesha.

Special Occasions and Deities:
* Amavasai Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs for the new moon day rituals.
* Pradosham Tamil Devotional Songs: Hymns for the auspicious Pradosham period.
* Ashta Lakshmi Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs dedicated to the eight forms of Goddess Lakshmi.
* Vinayagar Tamil Devotional Songs: Devotions for the remover of obstacles, Lord Vinayagar.
* Ganapathi Tamil Devotional Songs: Invoke blessings from Lord Ganapathi.
* Surya Tamil Devotional Songs: Worship the Sun God, Surya, with these melodies.
* Sani Tamil Devotional Songs: Appease Lord Sani with these devotional tracks.
* Guru Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs to honor Guru and seek his wisdom.
* Perumal Tamil Devotional Songs: Devote to Lord Perumal with these spiritual songs.
* Navagraha Tamil Devotional Songs: Balance your energies with songs for the nine planets.

Subscribe now and join our spiritual journey. Like, share, and hit the bell icon to stay updated with our latest devotional uploads. May these divine songs bring peace, prosperity, and positivity to your life.

snippet.title: Andhera Season 1 - Official Trailer | Prajakta Koli, Surveen Chawla, Priya Bapat, Karanvir Malhotra
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Andhera Season 1 Official Trailer
Starring Priya Bapat, Karanvir Malhotra, Prajakta Koli, Surveen Chawla, Vatsal Sheth, Parvin Dabas, Pranay Pachauri
Directed by Raaghav Dar
Written by Gaurav Desai, Raaghav Dar, Karan Anshuman, Chintan
Sarda, Akshat Ghildial, Karmanya Ahuja
Created by Gaurav Desai
Executive Producers: Ritesh Sidhwani, Farhan Akhtar, Kassim
Jagmagia, Mohit Shah, Karan Anshuman
Associate Producer: Vishal Ramchandani
Production Company: Excel Media and Entertainment LLP

Official Release Date Aug 14 2025, on Prime Video India.

About:
In the shadow of Mumbai's shimmering skyline, a sinister force
hunts the living. In this visceral tale of urban horror, a fearless cop
and a haunted medical student must take on this living darkness
to avert impending doom.

Follow us on:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/primevideoin/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PrimeVideoIN/
X: https://x.com/PrimeVideoIN

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages ‚Äì including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal ‚Äì The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video‚Äôs video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures ‚Äì Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

snippet.description:

snippet.title: Sri Varalakshmi Mangala Harathi Telugu | Sravanam Sukravaram Special | Lakshmi Devi Songs
snippet.description:
üå∫ Sri Varalakshmi Mangala Harathi ‚Äì A sacred and melodious Telugu devotional song dedicated to Goddess VaraLakshmi Devi, the goddess of wealth, prosperity, and auspiciousness.

Sri Varalakshmi Mangala Harathi Telugu,Varalakshmi Vratham Songs,Goddess Lakshmi Harathi,Sravana Sukravaram Special Songs,Lakshmi Devi Devotional Songs Telugu,Mangala Harathi Telugu Songs,Lakshmi Bhakti Songs,Varalakshmi Pooja Harathi,Friday Lakshmi Pooja Songs,Sravana Masam Special Bhakti Songs,Lakshmi Songs for Pooja,Telugu Devotional Songs for Goddess Lakshmi,Lakshmi Devi Songs Telugu,SriVaralakshmiMangalaHarathi,VaralakshmiDeviSongs,SravanamSukravaramSpecial

Lyrics:Traditioanl
Composer: Ghatti Sri Vidya
Singer: Ghatti Srividya

This divine Harathi song is specially offered on Sravana Sukravaram (Fridays in the month of Sravana), which holds immense spiritual significance in South Indian tradition. snippet.title: COOLIE Trailer Reaction! With Vivan & Brandon | Rajinikanth | Nagarjuna Akkineni | Aamir Khan
snippet.description:
Vivan and Brandon react to the explosive trailer for Coolie, marking the fiery return of Rajinikanth in a mass-loaded, emotional action drama.

Directed by Lokesh Kanagaraj (Leo, Vikram), Coolie brings back Rajinikanth (Jailer, Kaala) in a powerful new avatar‚Äîmixing grit, style, and legacy. With Anirudh Ravichander‚Äôs pulse-pounding score and stunning visuals, the film promises high-octane action and deep-rooted emotion.

Vivan and Brandon break down the intensity, vintage Rajini swag, and Lokesh‚Äôs signature world-building. Coolie looks like a full-blown cinematic celebration of one of India‚Äôs biggest icons.

____________________

snippet.title: Vhala Aavo Gokul Gam - 4K Video - Gopal Bharwad - Jigar Studio
snippet.description:
Song: Vhala Aavo Gokul Gam
Singer: Gopal Bharwad
Artists: Vijay Desai, Aarti Suthar, Hemali Gohil, Sanjay Pandya, Hasmukh Limbachiya
Music: Vishal Vagheshwari, Sunil Vagheshwari
Lyrics: Sahar Rabari
BGM: Rajendrasinh
Co - Ordinator: Indar Gamara
D.O.P. - Edit: Montu Rajput
Director: Vishnu Thakor - Adalaj
Producer: Gunvant Thakor
Music Label & Copyright: Jigar Studio

Lyrics Of This Song:

Kok Di Aavo Gokuliye Gam
Ke Kano Aaj Hambhare Chhe
He Vhala Aavo Gokuliye Gam
Ke Aaj Kano Hambhare Chhe
He Rove Chodhare Aakhuy Gam
Ke Kanho Kyare Aave Chhe
Ae Balpana Ni Gothano Ni Maya Meli Re
Kon Amaru Thashe Tara Vagar Meli Re
Vage Vage Hatey Hara Na Sur
Toye Pag Na Upade Re
He Mane Rahade Ramade Kon
Ke Kanho Aaj Hambhare Chhe

Pan Hari, Ae Hari Vagar Aa Het Kya Vechava
Are Re Mara Gani Ne Karya Te Vegada
Are Re Te To Karya Chhe Aaj Vegada
He Melya Kaleje Pana Na Bhar
Ke Yaad Tari Kanade Chhe
He Bhale Lakho Var Bhuliye Tara Nam
Toye Kajale Lay Lage Chhe
Amara Rakhya Ma Khot Kya Khataki Re
Hachu Na Bolo To Gala Na Ham Tamane
He Vhala Aavo Vrundavan Aaj
Maro Kano Mane Hambhare Chhe
Nidhivane Gopiyu Juve Tari Vat
Kanudo Aaj Hambhare Chhe

Pan Ame Dahya, Ae Dahya Ganda Thai Fariye
Are Re Hau Ne Jivataye Mua Lagiye
Are Re Ame Jivata Pan Mua Lagiye
He Aaj Mota Lai Betho Hashe Kam
Ke Kal Kanho Aavashe Re
Ha Eva Dal Ne Dalaha Dai
Aa Dan Mara Jay Chhe Re
Barsana Dungar Jovu Vatadi Re
Hu To Dungariye Chadi Jovu Vatadi Re
He Kanji Kanji Kari Modha Hukay
Pan Kanho Kya Hambhare Chhe
Tane To Badhu Hasya Ma Jay
Ahiya Jiv Maro Jay Chhe Re
Ha Eto Vite Ene Vedanayu Thay
Makhan Na Morari Re
Ha Kevi Munjhani Hashu Man Ma
Barsana Jovu Vatadi Re

snippet.description:

A divine expression of longing, love, and surrender. This is not just a song - it is a celebration of Prem Bhakti. Indresh Upadhyay Ji lends his devotional voice to a heartfelt music by B Praak and Mir Desai and beautifully inacted by Adrija Roy.

‚ñ∫ About Kripa Records:

"Kripa Records" is a devotional music label dedicated to producing and promoting spiritual music that inspires profound experiences. "Kripa" meaning "grace" in Sanskrit, reflects the essence of divine mercy in the label's music. Kripa‚Äôs diverse devotional music is crafted by renowned artists, invoking peace, reverence, and spiritual awakening. It will serve as a cherished companion for meditation, prayer, and reflection.

Humare Avm Gana Channel mein Chhatishgarhi Hits Gana aap logo ke liye prastut karte hain. Hum Chahte hain ki har baar aapke pasand ka New Cg Song aap logo ko de. 
Hume apne comment me bataye Chhattisgarhi Geet kisake aawaz me sunana chahte avam video dekhana chahte hain. Hum Humare gana ko Dj Version mein bhi layenge, hum humare Avm Gana Me hit chhattisgarhi gana dene ke liye pratibaddh hain. 
Hum humare Chhattisgarhi geet ko badhava dene wale singer & actor Tijan bai, Usha Barle, Mamta Chandrakar, Anuj sharma, Nitin Dubey, Dilip shadangi, Alka Chandrakar, chaya Chandrakar, Bhupendra sahu, Mithilesh sahu, Kuleshwar tamrakar , Kavita Vaishanvi, Sunil Soni,
Kanchan joshi, Sarla Gandharw, Anupma mishra, Sunny pandey, Dilip Ray, Shashi Rangila, Virendra Chaturvedi, Shyam Kuteliya, Karan Chauhan, Kiran Chauhan, Monika Verma, Seema Kaushik, Gorelal Barman, Garima Diwakar, Dilip Lahariya, Devesh Dahariya
Mann Quereshi, Anikriti Chauhan, Amlesh Nagesh, isi tarah chhattisgarh ke hum sabhi any singer avam actor ko tahe dil se Dhanywaad Karte hain. Jo Humari Chhattisgarhi Boli ko Desh va Videsh me Badhava De Rahe Hain...

Contact for Recording - AVM Audio & Video Studio, Near L.I.C. Building Shree Nagar  Khamtarai, Raipur (C.G) MO - 09301523929



Humare Avm Gana Channel mein Chhatishgarhi Hits Gana aap logo ke liye prastut karte hain. Hum Chahte hain ki har baar aapke pasand ka New Cg Song aap logo ko de. 
Hume apne comment me bataye Chhattisgarhi Geet kisake aawaz me sunana chahte avam video dekhana chahte hain. Hum Humare gana ko Dj Version mein bhi layenge, hum humare Avm Gana Me hit chhattisgarhi gana dene ke liye pratibaddh hain. 
Hum humare Chhattisgarhi geet ko badhava dene wale singer & actor Tijan bai, Usha Barle, Mamta Chandrakar, Anuj sharma, Nitin Dubey, Dilip shadangi, Alka Chandrakar, chaya Chandrakar, Bhupendra sahu, Mithilesh sahu, Kuleshwar tamrakar , Kavita Vaishanvi, Sunil Soni,
Kanchan joshi, Sarla Gandharw, Anupma mishra, Sunny pandey, Dilip Ray, Shashi Rangila, Virendra Chaturvedi, Shyam Kuteliya, Karan Chauhan, Kiran Chauhan, Monika Verma, Seema Kaushik, Gorelal Barman, Garima Diwakar, Dilip Lahariya, Devesh Dahariya
Mann Quereshi, Anikriti Chauhan, Amlesh Nagesh, isi tarah chhattisgarh ke hum sabhi any singer avam actor ko tahe dil se Dhanywaad Karte hain. Jo Humari Chhattisgarhi Boli ko Desh va Videsh me Badhava De Rahe Hain...
